Instead of taking the time to edit the crap out of that picture why don't you take that time instead to clean your bathroom and edit the crap out of your life. Listen I know you're busy OK we all got stuff but you gotta keep in mind, I don't care. Make time to finish the things you want to finish, make time to see the things you wanna see, and make time for other people and if your brain starts getting all wishy-washy with excuses think about how good it feels when other people make time for you.
